<h2>Summary</h2>
<%= infotab_header(['Project','Description','Kind','Size','Languages'] ) %>
	<%= render(:partial => 'revision', :object=>@revision, :locals=>{:brief=>false}) %>
</table>
<br />
<h2>Bidding Information</h2>
<%= infotab_header(['Maximal bid amount','Time to complete the work']) %>
	<tr>
		<td><span><%= @revision.max_bid %></span> <span><%= @revision.currency.disp_name.html_safe %></span> <span><%= @revision.payment_units %></span></td>
		<td>This job must be completed within <%= @revision.project_completion_duration %> days from the time a bid is accepted.</td>
 	</tr>
</table>
<br />
<% if @revision.kind == TA_PROJECT %>
<h2>Translation System</h2>
<p>All translations will be done using our translation system. This system will extract texts from the website and let you translate in-context. For more information, see the <a target="_blank" href="http://translators.icanlocalize.com">translator's zone</a>.</p>
<br />
<% end %>
<h2>How to Bid</h2>
<p>If you already have an account, <%= link_to('log in', {:controller=>:login}) %>. Otherwise, you're welcome to <%= link_to('sign up', {:controller=>:users, :action=>:new, :utype=>'Translator'}) %> and create an account.</p>
<div class="errorExplanation">
<h3>Our standard requirements from translators</h3>
<ul><li>You must have a university degree in translation or have passed the American Translators Association exam. We will ask you to upload a scan your degree.</li>
<li>We must be able to verify your identity. We can accept a scan of your ID document, a verified PayPal account or if you come from proz.com, we can verify your identity using your proz profile.</li>
<% if @revision.kind == TA_PROJECT %>
<li>You will need to do small practice project. This project is not meant to test your language skills but to familiarize you with our translation system.</li>
<% end %>
</ul>
</div>
<p>If you have any questions, please <%= link_to('contact us','http://www.icanlocalize.com/web_dialogs/new?language_id=1&amp;store=4') %>.</p>
<br />
<hr />
<br />
<p>Back to the list of <%= link_to('open projects', {:action=>:index}) %>.</p>